title: $10 Weekend Car Rentals from Enterprise
text:
$10 Weekend Car Rentals from Enterprise $10 Weekend Car Rentals from Enterprise   5:36 PM Tweet 
Pack in as much as you can during the weekend because Enterprise Rent-a-Car has rentals for less than $10 per day from Fridays through Mondays. Pick up an economy or compact car by May 23, 2016, and pay only $9.99. 
  To get the discount, visit the Weekend Special page at Enterprise's website. $14.99 per day applies to an intermediate car, $17.99 per day applies to a standard car, and $19.99 per day applies to a full-size car. 
The fine print: The promotion only includes 100 miles per day. The quoted rate doesn't include taxes, fees, or insurance coverage.
